VISIT THIS PAGE

https://nodejs.org/en/

and download the required version as per your requirement


After installation node will be installed in
Node.js v11.14.0 to /usr/local/bin/node
 and npm will be installed in
 npm v6.7.0 to /usr/local/bin/npm

To update npm to some other version,we can use this command
sudo npm install npm@6.9.0 -g
